ef="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">Oasis</a>的《Don’t Look Back In Anger》。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-suki-waterhouse-bring-out-jane-penny-to-cover-tops-in-montreal-3824480">观看 Suki Waterhouse 邀请 Jane Penny 登上蒙特利尔 TOPS 封面的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
