w.youtube.com/embed/E1vhcB4xLO8?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Billie Eilish“祝自己圣诞快乐”2024 年 12 月 16 日起亚论坛@BillieEilish" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/OZDD9pP3bQ4?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="2024.12.17 加利福尼亚州洛杉矶 Billie Eilish - 银铃" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/j5H26WfjWfY?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="比莉·艾利什昨晚在洛杉矶表演《平安夜》" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/feKcaWoak5E?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Billie Eilish 在论坛上演唱“O Holy Night”" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/652GjJMW_fU?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在洛杉矶的一场演出中，Eilish 还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-billie-eilish-bring-out-charli-xcx-to-perform-guess-remix-in-la-3823303">邀请了 Charli XCX 作为特邀嘉宾来表演他们的“Guess”混音版</a>。</p><p>该曲目获得<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grammys-nominations-2025-check-out-the-full-list-of-nominations-here-3811039">2025 年格莱美奖</a>最佳流行二重奏/团体表演提名。两位艺术家还角逐年度专辑、年度唱片、最佳流行独奏表演等奖项。</p><p>其他新闻方面，艾利什最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-plays-snippet-of-fun-new-songs-weve-been-making-music-3821114">在一次采访中播放了两首新歌的片段，并透露她又开始“创作音乐”了</a>。</p><p>在其他地方，Eilish 和 Finneas <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-billie-eilish-and-finneas-perform-one-of-our-favourite-songs-that-weve-ever-written-on-tiny-desk-3821859">出现在 NPR 的 Tiny Desk 上，并以深度剪辑“I Love You”的形式回顾了她的首张 LP，令粉丝们感到惊讶</a>。</p><p>她的歌曲《Birds Of A Feather》最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/lists/end-of-year/best-songs-2024">被<i>NME</i>评为 2024 年最佳歌曲第 12 名</a>。她的专辑《Hit Me Hard And Soft》也入围<em>NME</em> <a href="https://www.nme.com/lists/end-of-year/best-albums-2024-3818995">2024 年最佳专辑排行榜，排名第九</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-billie-eilish-cover-o-holy-night-at-los-angeles-show-3824457">Watch Billie Eilish 在洛杉矶演出中翻唱的歌曲《O Holy Night》</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
